                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/8066" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">STR-2026</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">1931 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">节能减排，拔地倚天：中天科技光纤的绿色低碳之路</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Energy saving and emission reduction, pull from the ground and rely on the sky: The green and low-carbon path of Zhongtian Technology optical fiber</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">张敏，沈婕，张瑾瑜，刘蕊畅，姜朝晖，曹越</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">南通大学*</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中天科技光纤有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">通讯业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">环保部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">14 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中天科技光纤有限公司；战略管理；低碳环保；绿色转型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Zhongtian Technology Fiber Optic Co., Ltd.; Strategic management; Low carbon environmental protection; Green transformation</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">为贯彻落实国家碳达峰、碳中和战略，满足客户在绿色制造资质方面逐步提高的要求，中天科技光纤有限公司决定开启绿色转型之路，开展各项绿色低碳工作。本案例以安环总监陆亮亮的视角展开，主要讲述了中天科技光纤提前布局实施绿色转型，积极进行组织改革，全面推行绿色制造，数字赋能绿色变革，助力双碳目标实现。绿色制造是制造业转型升级的必由之路，也是实现“绿色化”发展的关键举措，本案例重点介绍了中天科技光纤从绿色设计、绿色生产、绿色包装、绿色采购、绿色物流、绿色生活、绿色能源这七个方面实施绿色制造的路径，描述了过程中遇到的阻碍以及具体的解决方案，并展望绿色转型的未来发展方向。本案例对于大型企业如何进行战略规划与绿色转型具有重要的借鉴意义。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">To implement the national strategy for carbon neutrality and meet the increasing demands of customers for green manufacturing qualifications, Zhongtian Technology Fiber Opti Co., Ltd. has decided to pursue green transformation and carry out various green and low-carbon initiatives. The following account is from the perspective of Lu Liangliang, director of Anhuan, it primarily describes how Zhongtian Technology Fiber Optic Co., Ltd. laid out and implemented green transformation in advance, actively carried out organizational reforms, fully promoted green manufacturing, digitally empowered of green changes, and helped achieve the dual carbon goals. Green manufacturing is essential for the transformation and upgrading the manufacturing industry, as well as a key measure to achieve sustainable development. This case study focuses on the implementation of green manufacturing in seven key areas: green design, green production, green packaging, green procurement, green logistics, green lifestyle, and green energy by Zhongtian Technology Fiber Optic Co., Ltd. It also describes the obstacles encountered in the process, specific solutions, and the future direction of green transformation. This case study is a valuable reference for large enterprises on how to carry out strategic planning and green transformation.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2022</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《战略管理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">波特假说；动态能力观；组织惯性；绿色全产业链；敏捷组织</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
